page.title: 14John Barrett from Withybrook
page.content: { John Barrett}has lived in Withybrook for a year.He is a pupil at{St.James {School,in Bulkington}where he used to live.He would prefer to live in Bulkington to Withybrook.He only has about 2 friends where he lives .They are not the same age as he.There are no clubs in Withybrook for his age or for adults.His hobbies are fishing and stamp collecting.There is a small pond where he goes fishing.Nearby is a small playing field. It has no swings or slides.He goes to church regularly. The village isn't very quiet-there are always people doing odd jobs. Because he comes to school in Bulkington his mum and dad drop him off at his gran's house and he walks from there.His dad works in{Bedworth {for British Telecom}.His mum works in Coventry for{Coventry Leisure {Services.
